#

Balsamic Vinaigrette

5 min
$2.5
85 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 8

Dietary Tags:

VeganGluten-Free

Cuisine:

Italian

Course:

Condiment

Tags:

DressingSaladEasy

Description

A classic, tangy dressing that elevates any salad with ease!

Ingredients

  • balsamic vinegar: 1/4 cup
  • extra virgin olive oil: 3/4 cup
  • dijon mustard: 1 teaspoon
  • honey or maple syrup (optional): 1 teaspoon
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
